%h2
  A Mind for Management

%h4  
  A six-week development programme for line managers

%p
  Strong managers are essential to any successful organisation. Excellent line managers attract exceptional staff, motivate people to succeed, increase innovation and lead happy and successful teams. Yet many line managers are struggling with increased pressure and asking more from their people. From motivation to innovation, modern managers need to understand management psychology to get the best from their staff.

%p
  This six-week programme teaches managers about the psychology of management. Delivered in six 90-minute masterclasses, perfect for high-pressure environments, this programme is aimed at anyone with line management responsibilities, particularly new managers, and provides an essential grounding on managing people and developing teams. 

